320
00:34:16.843 --> 00:34:21.043
Aceastïŋ― ïŋ―ncïŋ―pere nu are
nevoie de lecïŋ―ii de istorie. reginïŋ―.

321
00:34:21.243 --> 00:34:23.543
Atunci care e lecïŋ―ia
pe care doreïŋ―ti sïŋ― o auzi?

322
00:34:23.643 --> 00:34:25.943
Vrei sïŋ― ïŋ―i le enumïŋ―r
