323
00:34:26.043 --> 00:34:29.543
Onoare. datorie. glorie.

324
00:34:29.643 --> 00:34:32.243
Tu vorbeïŋ―ti de onoare?

325
00:34:32.343 --> 00:34:34.943
Datorie? Glorie?

326
00:34:35.943 --> 00:34:37.643
Dar cum rïŋ―mïŋ―ne
cu adulterul?

327
00:34:37.743 --> 00:34:40.343
- Cum ïŋ―ndrïŋ―zneïŋ―ti?
- Cum ïŋ―ndrïŋ―znesc?

328
00:34:40.443 --> 00:34:43.443
Priviïŋ―i-o cu atenïŋ―ie.

329
00:34:43.443 --> 00:34:46.643
E o mincinoasïŋ― perfectïŋ―.

330
00:34:46.643 --> 00:34:50.143
Nu te juca cu membrii acestui
consiliu sacru. reginïŋ―.

331
00:34:50.143 --> 00:34:53.243
Doar cu cïŋ―teva ore ïŋ―n urmïŋ―.
mi te-ai oferit.

332
00:34:53.343 --> 00:34:57.743
Dacïŋ― aïŋ― fi fost mai slab.
i-aïŋ― purta ïŋ―ncïŋ― parfumul.

333
00:34:57.843 --> 00:35:01.043
- Asta e o insultïŋ―.
- Vorbeïŋ―te ipocritul.

334
00:35:01.043 --> 00:35:03.043
N-ai primit ïŋ―i tu
asemenea rïŋ―splatïŋ―?

335
00:35:03.143 --> 00:35:07.643
Pe care ai acceptat-o ïŋ―n schimbul
acordïŋ―rii unei audienïŋ―e la aceïŋ―ti nobili?

336
00:35:07.643 --> 00:35:09.443
- E o minciunïŋ―?
- Este?

337
00:35:09.543 --> 00:35:13.743
N-a venit el. la invitaïŋ―ia ta.
ïŋ―n dormitorul regelui?

338
00:35:13.743 --> 00:35:16.743
Acelaïŋ―i pat ïŋ―n care
ai ïŋ―ncercat sïŋ― negociezi cu mine

339
00:35:16.743 --> 00:35:19.443
atïŋ―t de energic.

340
00:35:21.243 --> 00:35:22.943
Pïŋ―reïŋ―i ïŋ―ocaïŋ―i.

341
00:35:22.943 --> 00:35:24.643
O mitïŋ― carnalïŋ―. domnilor.

342
00:35:24.643 --> 00:35:28.543
ïŋ―n timp ce soïŋ―ul ei ïŋ―ncurajeazïŋ―
anarhia ïŋ―i rïŋ―zboiul!

343
00:35:32.643 --> 00:35:35.843
Cuvintele scapïŋ― chiar ïŋ―i
celor mai iscusite limbi.

344
00:35:36.343 --> 00:35:38.843
Mica mea reginïŋ― tïŋ―rfïŋ―.

345
00:35:43.043 --> 00:35:45.743
Ce comportament de reginïŋ―!

346
00:35:46.443 --> 00:35:49.743
Scoateïŋ―i-o de aici ïŋ―nainte
sïŋ― ne ïŋ―ntineze ïŋ―i mai tare

347
00:35:49.843 --> 00:35:53.343
cu prezenïŋ―a ei josnicïŋ―
ïŋ―i murdarïŋ―.

348
00:35:59.243 --> 00:36:01.943
Asta nu se va termina repede.

349
00:36:02.443 --> 00:36:04.743
N-o sïŋ―-ïŋ―i placïŋ―.

350
00:36:04.743 --> 00:36:07.043
Nu sunt regina ta.

351
00:36:28.443 --> 00:36:30.043
Trïŋ―dïŋ―tor.

352
00:36:30.943 --> 00:36:33.043
Trïŋ―dïŋ―tor. trïŋ―dïŋ―tor.

353
00:37:14.943 --> 00:37:18.543
Leonidas.
Complimentele mele.

354
00:37:18.643 --> 00:37:20.943
ïŋ―i felicitïŋ―ri.

355
00:37:21.243 --> 00:37:24.743
ïŋ―i-ai transformat
dezastrul ïŋ―n victorie.

356
00:37:24.843 --> 00:37:28.343
ïŋ―n ciuda aroganïŋ―ei tale
insuportabile.

357
00:37:28.343 --> 00:37:31.643
Regele Zeu a venit sïŋ― admire
vitejia spartanïŋ―

358
00:37:31.743 --> 00:37:33.043
ïŋ―i calitïŋ―ïŋ―ile combative.

359
00:37:33.143 --> 00:37:34.443
Vei fi un aliat puternic.

360
00:37:34.443 --> 00:37:36.843
Supune-te. Leonidas.

361
00:37:37.243 --> 00:37:41.343
Foloseïŋ―te-ïŋ―i raïŋ―iunea.
Gïŋ―ndeïŋ―te-te la oamenii tïŋ―i.

362
00:37:43.443 --> 00:37:45.343
Te implor.

363
00:37:45.443 --> 00:37:47.343
Ascultïŋ―-l pe compatriotul
tïŋ―u grec.

364
00:37:47.443 --> 00:37:51.343
El ïŋ―ïŋ―i poate dovedi
generozitatea Regelui Divin.

365
00:37:51.543 --> 00:37:54.143
ïŋ―n ciuda insultelor tale
repetate.

366
00:37:54.143 --> 00:37:57.243
ïŋ―n ciuda blasfemiilor
tale ïŋ―ngrozitoare.

367
00:37:57.243 --> 00:38:00.343
domnul oïŋ―tirilor e pregïŋ―tit
sïŋ― vïŋ― ierte tot.

368
00:38:00.443 --> 00:38:03.743
ïŋ―i mai mult: sïŋ― ïŋ―ïŋ―i rïŋ―splïŋ―teascïŋ―
serviciile.

369
00:38:03.743 --> 00:38:07.143
Lupïŋ―i pentru pïŋ―mïŋ―nturile
tale. Pïŋ―streazïŋ―-le.

370
00:38:07.943 --> 00:38:10.243
Lupïŋ―i pentru Sparta.

371
00:38:10.243 --> 00:38:14.043
Va fi mai bogatïŋ―
ïŋ―i mai puternicïŋ― ca oricïŋ―nd.

372
00:38:14.443 --> 00:38:17.143
Te lupïŋ―i pentru tronul tïŋ―u.

373
00:38:17.143 --> 00:38:20.243
Vei fi proclamat stïŋ―pïŋ―n
al Greciei.

374
00:38:20.243 --> 00:38:24.843
Vei rïŋ―spunde doar ïŋ―n faïŋ―a unicului
ïŋ―i adevïŋ―ratului stïŋ―pïŋ―n al lumii.

375
00:38:24.843 --> 00:38:29.743
Leonidas. Victoria ta
va fi completïŋ―.

376
00:38:29.743 --> 00:38:35.743
Doar dacïŋ― depui armele
ïŋ―i ïŋ―ngenunchezi ïŋ―n faïŋ―a divinului Xerxes.

377
00:39:06.343 --> 00:39:11.243
<i>Au trecut mai bine de 30 de ani
de la vïŋ―narea lupului ïŋ―n frigul iernii.</i>

378
00:39:11.343 --> 00:39:16.343
<i>Acum. ca ïŋ―i atunci. nu teama
ïŋ―l cuprinde.</i>

379
00:39:16.343 --> 00:39:18.143
<i>Doar neastïŋ―mpïŋ―rul.</i>

380
00:39:18.243 --> 00:39:21.743
<i>O intensificare a simïŋ―urilor.</i>

381
00:39:22.343 --> 00:39:27.343
<i>Briza rïŋ―coroasïŋ― a mïŋ―rii adiind
pe sudoarea-i de pe piept ïŋ―i gïŋ―t.</i>

382
00:39:27.343 --> 00:39:28.843
<i>Croncïŋ―nitul pescïŋ―ruïŋ―ilor.</i>

383
00:39:28.943 --> 00:39:33.243
<i>nemulïŋ―umiïŋ―i chiar ïŋ―i cïŋ―nd
se hrïŋ―nesc cu mii de morïŋ―i ce plutesc.</i>

384
00:39:34.643 --> 00:39:39.143
<i>Respiraïŋ―ia regulatïŋ―
a celor 300 din spatele sïŋ―u.</i>

385
00:39:40.643 --> 00:39:44.543
<i>Gata sïŋ― moarïŋ― pentru el.
fïŋ―rïŋ― ezitare.</i>

386
00:39:46.743 --> 00:39:52.243
<i>Fiecare din ei
gata sïŋ― moarïŋ―.</i>

387
00:40:07.043 --> 00:40:10.143
<i>Coiful ïŋ―l apasïŋ―.</i>

388
00:40:30.343 --> 00:40:33.343
<i>Scutul ïŋ―i e greu.</i>

389
00:40:40.643 --> 00:40:43.043
Suliïŋ―a ta.

390
00:40:51.243 --> 00:40:53.043
Tu de colo.

391
00:40:53.043 --> 00:40:55.343
Efialtes.

392
00:41:00.143 --> 00:41:02.643
Sïŋ― trïŋ―ieïŋ―ti veïŋ―nic.

393
00:41:09.943 --> 00:41:12.543
Leonidas. suliïŋ―a ta.

394
00:42:18.943 --> 00:42:22.043
Stelios!

395
00:42:30.843 --> 00:42:33.043
Masacraïŋ―i-i!

396
00:42:35.743 --> 00:42:39.443
<i>Coiful sïŋ―u ïŋ―l apïŋ―sa.
ïŋ―i limita vederea.</i>

397
00:42:39.543 --> 00:42:41.943
<i>ïŋ―i trebuia sïŋ― vadïŋ― departe.</i>

398
00:42:41.943 --> 00:42:45.843
<i>Scutul ïŋ―i era greu.
ïŋ―l dezechilibra.</i>

399
00:42:46.243 --> 00:42:50.143
<i>ïŋ―i ïŋ―inta lui e tare departe.</i>

400
00:43:54.443 --> 00:43:58.743
<i>Bïŋ―trïŋ―nii spun cïŋ― noi. spartanii.
suntem urmaïŋ―ii lui Hercule.</i>

401
00:44:00.543 --> 00:44:04.143
<i>Viteazul Leonidas stïŋ― mïŋ―rturie
a descendenïŋ―ei noastre.</i>

402
00:44:04.943 --> 00:44:09.743
<i>Strigïŋ―tul sïŋ―u e lung ïŋ―i puternic.</i>

403
00:44:39.243 --> 00:44:40.543
Regele meu.

404
00:44:53.143 --> 00:44:57.543
E o onoare
sïŋ― mor alïŋ―turi de tine.

405
00:44:58.343 --> 00:45:02.443
A fost o onoare sïŋ― trïŋ―iesc
alïŋ―turi de tine.

406
00:45:23.743 --> 00:45:26.143
Regina mea.

407
00:45:33.743 --> 00:45:36.043
Soïŋ―ia mea.

408
00:45:47.343 --> 00:45:49.543
Iubirea mea.

409
00:48:15.343 --> 00:48:17.343
<i>Amintiïŋ―i-vïŋ― de noi.</i>

410
00:48:19.143 --> 00:48:22.243
<i>Cel mai simplu ordin
pe care-l poate da un rege.</i>

411
00:48:24.243 --> 00:48:27.443
<i>Amintiïŋ―i-vïŋ― de ce am murit.</i>

412
00:48:29.243 --> 00:48:33.043
<i>Cïŋ―ci el n-a dorit omagii
sau cïŋ―ntece.</i>

413
00:48:35.043 --> 00:48:39.343
N-a dorit monumente
sau poeme de rïŋ―zboi ïŋ―i vitejie.

414
00:48:42.243 --> 00:48:44.643
Dorinïŋ―a lui a fost simplïŋ―.

415
00:48:49.943 --> 00:48:52.243
Amintiïŋ―i-vïŋ― de noi.

416
00:48:53.043 --> 00:48:55.343
Aïŋ―a mi-a spus.

417
00:48:56.443 --> 00:48:58.843
<i>Aceasta era speranïŋ―a lui.</i>

418
00:48:58.943 --> 00:49:03.243
<i>Dacïŋ― vreun suflet liber
va trece prin locurile acelea</i>

419
00:49:03.343 --> 00:49:07.243
<i>ïŋ―n nenumïŋ―ratele veacuri
ce au sïŋ― vie.</i>

420
00:49:07.343 --> 00:49:11.443
<i>fie ca glasurile noastre
sïŋ―-ïŋ―i ïŋ―opteascïŋ― din pietrele eterne.</i>

421
00:49:14.543 --> 00:49:18.343
<i>Mergi ïŋ―i spune-le spartanilor.
trecïŋ―torule.</i>

422
00:49:18.843 --> 00:49:24.843
<i>cïŋ― am murit aici
dupïŋ― legea spartanïŋ―.</i>

423
00:49:27.643 --> 00:49:30.243
<i>Aïŋ―a a murit regele meu.</i>

424
00:49:31.043 --> 00:49:33.743
<i>ïŋ―i fraïŋ―ii mei au murit.</i>

425
00:49:35.443 --> 00:49:38.543
Acum un an.

426
00:49:42.643 --> 00:49:48.043
Am cugetat ïŋ―ndelung la cuvintele
regelui meu despre victorie

427
00:49:48.043 --> 00:49:50.543
ïŋ―i timpul a dovedit
cïŋ― avea dreptate.

428
00:49:51.643 --> 00:49:54.843
Cïŋ―ci de la un grec liber
la altul.

429
00:49:54.843 --> 00:49:59.343
s-a rïŋ―spïŋ―ndit vestea cïŋ― viteazul
Leonidas ïŋ―i cei 300 ai sïŋ―i.

430
00:49:59.443 --> 00:50:01.643
atïŋ―t de departe de casïŋ―.

431
00:50:01.743 --> 00:50:05.043
ïŋ―i-au dat vieïŋ―ile.
nu numai pentru Sparta.

432
00:50:05.043 --> 00:50:09.643
ci pentru toatïŋ― Grecia
ïŋ―i promisiunea acesteia.

433
00:50:09.943 --> 00:50:15.043
ïŋ―i acum. aici pe acest petic
de pïŋ―mïŋ―nt numit Platea.

434
00:50:15.143 --> 00:50:19.743
hoardele lui Xerxes
ïŋ―i ïŋ―nfruntïŋ― sfïŋ―rïŋ―itul.

435
00:50:21.943 --> 00:50:25.243
Acolo se ïŋ―ngrïŋ―mïŋ―desc barbarii.

436
00:50:25.643 --> 00:50:28.743
Teroarea purïŋ― le cuprinde strïŋ―ns

437
00:50:29.043 --> 00:50:32.543
inimile lor cu degete de gheaïŋ―ïŋ―.

438
00:50:32.643 --> 00:50:35.943
Ei ïŋ―tiu prea bine ce grozïŋ―vii
sïŋ―lbatice au ïŋ―ndurat

439
00:50:35.943 --> 00:50:39.143
din cauza sïŋ―biilor
ïŋ―i suliïŋ―elor celor 300.

440
00:50:39.943 --> 00:50:43.243
Dar acum se uitïŋ―.
peste cïŋ―mpie.

441
00:50:43.243 --> 00:50:48.143
la 10.000 de spartani
care conduc 30.000 de greci liberi.

442
00:50:55.843 --> 00:50:59.743
Duïŋ―manul nostru e de trei
ori mai numeros ca noi.

443
00:50:59.943 --> 00:51:02.443
Sorïŋ―i favorabili grecilor.

444
00:51:02.843 --> 00:51:07.443
ïŋ―n aceastïŋ― zi. vom salva
lumea de misticism ïŋ―i tiranie

445
00:51:07.543 --> 00:51:11.243
ïŋ―i vom inaugura un viitor mai luminos
decïŋ―t orice ne putem imagina.

446
00:51:16.343 --> 00:51:18.443
Aduceïŋ―i mulïŋ―umiri...

447
00:51:18.443 --> 00:51:21.843
... lui Leonidas ïŋ―i a celor
trei sute de viteji ai sïŋ―i.

448
00:51:22.543 --> 00:51:25.743
Spre victorie!

